unmatchedTraits.name: Always Wanted to Camp
unmatchedTraits.description: I used to dream about sleeping under the stars. Used to.

unmatchedTraits.name: Awful Fashion Sense
unmatchedTraits.description: Orange is the perfect color. It goes with everything!

unmatchedTraits.name: Bead Crafter
unmatchedTraits.description: I sold my beadwork out of a little online store I ran myself.

unmatchedTraits.name: Broad-Shouldered
unmatchedTraits.description: You can carry a lot on a good set of shoulders.

unmatchedTraits.name: Bronto Gas Attendant
unmatchedTraits.description: The distinction is in the extinction!

unmatchedTraits.name: Changed Jobs a Lot
unmatchedTraits.description: Some of us never found our dream job. We just took whatever we could get.

unmatchedTraits.name: Cleaned Offices
unmatchedTraits.description: When I did my job right, no one knew I was there.

unmatchedTraits.name: Drove a Crappy Car
unmatchedTraits.description: I had this old car in high school that I swear broke down every week.

unmatchedTraits.name: Flinches at Noises
unmatchedTraits.description: Firing a gun is just awful for me. I can't seem to get used to the noise.

unmatchedTraits.name: Former Activist *A*
unmatchedTraits.description: I've always had to fight to protect those who couldn't protect themselves.

unmatchedTraits.name: Former Homeowner *A*
unmatchedTraits.description: I still get emotional when I think about all the equity we used to have.

unmatchedTraits.name: Had a Beloved Aunt
unmatchedTraits.description: She helped me to become the person I am today.

unmatchedTraits.name: Hates Trespassers
unmatchedTraits.description: My home is my castle. If you stop by, you'd better have an invitation.

unmatchedTraits.name: House Had Black Mold
unmatchedTraits.description: It was just once, but ever since I can't help but wash everything twice.

unmatchedTraits.name: Hyper-Prepared
unmatchedTraits.description: I never go outside without a week's worth of gear.

unmatchedTraits.name: Into Cheesy Movies
unmatchedTraits.description: And the sappier, the better.

unmatchedTraits.name: Into Nostalgia
unmatchedTraits.description: All the best stuff was made before I was born.

unmatchedTraits.name: Learned to Shop
unmatchedTraits.description: Ironic that it took the end of our consumer economy for me to pick this up.

unmatchedTraits.name: Likes Army Fatigues
unmatchedTraits.description: No, I was never in the army. I just really like khaki.

unmatchedTraits.name: Lived Amongst Celebrities
unmatchedTraits.description: I grew up in a town where everybody thought they were going to be famous.

unmatchedTraits.name: Lived at a High Altitude
unmatchedTraits.description: I don't know why you're out of breath. I used to get by on way less oxygen.

unmatchedTraits.name: Loved Being Single
unmatchedTraits.description: Dating just always seemed more fun to me than settling down.

unmatchedTraits.name: Loves to be Scared
unmatchedTraits.description: You've never more alive than when you're absolutely terrified.

unmatchedTraits.name: MCP Certified
unmatchedTraits.description: You should see all the Computers endorsements I have on my profile.

unmatchedTraits.name: No Belief in Destiny
unmatchedTraits.description: There is no fate but what we make for ourselves.

unmatchedTraits.name: No Belief in Fairness
unmatchedTraits.description: Life is pain. Anyone who tells you differently is selling something.

unmatchedTraits.name: Part-time Barista
unmatchedTraits.description: Actually, I was a screenwriter. Making coffee just paid the bills.

unmatchedTraits.name: Played Soccer
unmatchedTraits.description: I still miss the orange wedges.

unmatchedTraits.name: Practices Ikebana
unmatchedTraits.description: It's a Japanese style of flower arrangement. I can show you how to do it.

unmatchedTraits.name: Raised by Single Mom
unmatchedTraits.description: I don't know how she did it, but somehow she managed to get me this far.

unmatchedTraits.name: Ran a Medical Office
unmatchedTraits.description: I was never formally trained in medicine, but I was around it a lot.

unmatchedTraits.name: Ready for Anything
unmatchedTraits.description: I'm always pumped. I can handle whatever you throw at me.

unmatchedTraits.name: Scammed an Employer
unmatchedTraits.description: *Unknown*

unmatchedTraits.name: Self-Conscious
unmatchedTraits.description: Does this backpack make my butt look big?

unmatchedTraits.name: Self-Effacing
unmatchedTraits.description: I couldnâ€™t do it without you guys.

unmatchedTraits.name: Sewage System Operator
unmatchedTraits.description: When you've seen what I've seen, you understand the value of keeping clean.

unmatchedTraits.name: Sheriff's Deputy
unmatchedTraits.description: Out where I was, the sidearm was mostly for snakes and coyotes.

unmatchedTraits.name: Sings Badly in Public
unmatchedTraits.description: We have literally nothing to lose. We should all be singing, all the time.

unmatchedTraits.name: Slumming Mechanic
unmatchedTraits.description: It was just a job to pay the bills. I don't really even like cars.

unmatchedTraits.name: Spent Weekends Antiquing
unmatchedTraits.description: You should see some of the treasures I found over the years.

unmatchedTraits.name: Stays Fit
unmatchedTraits.description: Keeping in shape always came a little easier for me. I don't even exercise.

unmatchedTraits.name: Survivor's Guilt
unmatchedTraits.description: I'm not even supposed to be alive. Somebody else should be here, not me.

unmatchedTraits.name: Taught Elementary School
unmatchedTraits.description: *Unknown*

unmatchedTraits.name: Tells Bad Jokes *A*
unmatchedTraits.description: Have you heard the one about the gorilla who couldn't tell time?

unmatchedTraits.name: Used to be Reckless
unmatchedTraits.description: It's best that you didn't know me when I was younger.

unmatchedTraits.name: Used to Paint
unmatchedTraits.description: It used to help me relax after a long, hard day of not-painting.

unmatchedTraits.name: Used to the Cold
unmatchedTraits.description: You guys have never even seen real cold. I used to shovel two feet of snow.

unmatchedTraits.name: Veteran Gambler
unmatchedTraits.description: Call it, heads or tails?

unmatchedTraits.name: Video Game Producer
unmatchedTraits.description: My job is essentially herding cats. Well-armed, apocalypse-surviving cats.

unmatchedTraits.name: Was in ROTC
unmatchedTraits.description: I did some military training in school, but never got around to enlisting.

unmatchedTraits.name: Worked at an Office
unmatchedTraits.description: Honesty, I have trouble explaining what I did all day at work.

unmatchedTraits.name: Worked on a Farm
unmatchedTraits.description: I worked summers picking berries on my best friend's dad's farm.

unmatchedTraits.name: Worked at Tartan Mart
unmatchedTraits.description: Hi, welcome to Tartan Mart, how can I help you today?

unmatchedTraits.name: World War II Buff
unmatchedTraits.description: It was a simpler time, when it was easier to tell friend from foe.
